  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Grill the fish for 4-5 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "3. Warm the tortilla wrap in the microwave for 10-15 seconds.",
    "4. Spread the zanzibari sauce on the tortilla wrap.",
    "5. Add sliced cucumber, chopped cilantro, and grilled fish on top.",
    "6. Drizzle with lemon juice and sprinkle with salt, pepper, and chili powder (if using).",
    "7. Fold the tortilla wrap to enclose the filling.",
    "8. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
